==English==
===Noun===
'''fritter'''

# A type of food made by [[deep frying]] a [[batter]].  The batter may also contain fruit (e.g. [[apple fritter]]), vegetable (e.g. [[corn fritter]]), [[seafood]] (e.g. [[clam fritter]]), or other foods.
====See also====
*[[tempura]]

===Intransitive verb===
#To occupy oneself idly or without clear purpose, to [[fiddle]] with an unimportant part of a project, to [[dally]], perhaps to [[procrastinate]].  Often used with [[around]] or [[about]].
#:''I was supposed to do work, but I frittered around all afternoon.''
#:''He can't figure out how to finish the paper he's writing, so he's resorted to frittering with the fonts.''

